<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>CSE Motors</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" media="screen">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <header>
      <h1>CSE Motors</h1>
      <a href="#" class="account-link">My Account</a>
    </header>

    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Custom</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Sedan</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">SUV</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Truck</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <h2>Welcome to CSE Motors!</h2>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h3>DMC Delorean</h3>
          <p>3 Cup holders<br/>Superman doors<br/>Fuzzy dice!</p>
          <a href="#" class="cta-button">Own Today</a>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/vehicles/delorean.jpg" alt="DMC Delorean" />
      </section>

      <section class="cards">
        <div class="upgrades">
              <h3>Delorean Upgrades</h3>
              <ul>
                    <li>
                          <a href="#">
                                <div class="upgrade-item">
                                      <img src="/images/upgrades/flux-cap.png" alt="Flux Capacitor" />
                                </div>
                                <span>Flux Capacitor</span>
                          </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                          <a href="#">
                                <div class="upgrade-item">
                                      <img src="/images/upgrades/flame.jpg" alt="Flame Decals" />
                                </div>
                                <span>Flame Decals</span>
                          </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                          <a href="#">
                                <div class="upgrade-item">
                                      <img src="/images/upgrades/bumper_sticker.jpg" alt="Bumper Stickers" />
                                </div>
                                <span>Bumper Stickers</span>
                          </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                          <a href="#">
                                <div class="upgrade-item">
                                      <img src="/images/upgrades/hub-cap.jpg" alt="Hub Caps" />
                                </div>
                                <span>Hub Caps</span>
                          </a>
                    </li>
              </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews">
              <h3>DMC Delorean Reviews</h3>
              <ul>
                    <li>“So fast it’s almost like traveling in time.” (4/5)</li>
                    <li>“Coolest ride on the road.” (4/5)</li>
                    <li>“I’m feeling McFly!” (5/5)</li>
                    <li>“The most futuristic ride of our day.” (4.5/5)</li>
                    <li>“80’s livin and I love it!” (5/5)</li>
              </ul>
        </div>
  </section>

    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2025, CSE 340 App</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
